This interactive map displays cafés and mountain peaks within the city of Salzburg. Cafés are clustered to improve readability and expand as you zoom in, allowing easy exploration of local spots. Mountain peaks are marked with distinct icons. The map includes customized zoom limits to ensure an optimal viewing experience, preventing excessive zooming in or out. Popups show café names and peak details, with café names highlighted in bold for quick identification. Tooltips provide instant info on hover, enhancing usability. This map is ideal for both tourists and locals who want to discover charming cafés and scenic peaks around Salzburg.
